== X10 Controller system

This simple Rails app provides a RESTful system for accessing X10 equipment using the ActiveHome SDK via the web.

== Features

 * Iphone support
 * Exteremly simple
 * Tested
 
== Requirements

 * ActiveHome SDK
 * Windows
 
== Installation

 Extract and edit app/models/unit.rb and set the path to ActiveHome.
 Ensure your equipment is connected and start the server.
 
